# Fed-Med-FL

Proiect dizertatie cu Federated Learning:
- 3 noduri (spitale) + 1 nod central

## Structura
- services/central: orchestrator + aggregator + registry global
- services/node/api: gateway local (FastAPI)
- services/node/worker: job runner (Celery)
- services/node/ui: Node Portal (Next.js)
- shared/python/node_core: cod comun (ML/FL utils)

## Quick start
1) Pornire servicii:
   make up
2) Oprire:
   make down

Central: http://localhost:8080/health
Node1 API: http://localhost:8001/api/health
Node1 UI: http://localhost:3001
